%N A396045 a(n) = T(n, 2*n), where T(n, m) is the forward-difference table of the Catalan numbers.
%C A396045 This is the r = 2 case of the family a_r(n) = T(n, r*n), where T is the forward-difference table of the Catalan numbers. The cases r = 0 and r = 1 give A005043 and A220097, respectively.
%F A396045 a(n) = T(n, 2*n), where T(0, m) = A000108(m) and T(n, m) = T(n - 1, m + 1) - T(n - 1, m) for n>0.
%F A396045 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} (-1)^(n - k)*binomial(n, k)*A000108(2*n + k).
%F A396045 a(n) = (2/Pi)*Integral_{t=0..1} sqrt((1-t)/t)*(64*t^3-16*t^2)^n dt.
